# Settings Feature

## Overview
The Settings screen manages app preferences, user profile, notifications, theme, and data export functionality.

## Screen Structure

### SettingsScreen (Main)
- **Location**: `lib/features/settings/settings_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - Header with "Settings" title
  - User profile section (avatar, name, email)
  - Settings menu items (list of tiles)
  - Logout button (red, bottom)

### NotificationsScreen
- **Location**: `lib/features/settings/notifications_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - Back button
  - List of notification toggles
  - Each toggle: label + switch/checkbox

