- Each setting: 16px vertical padding
- Label: 14px, regular
- Toggle: right-aligned

### Logout Button
- Width: 100%
- Height: 48px
- Background: red-100 (light) / red-900/30 (dark)
- Text: red-500, bold
- Border radius: 12px
- Margin: 24px top
- Active scale: 0.95

